1192
01:44:42,250 --> 01:44:43,250
<i>Eckhart, escuto.</i>

1193
01:44:50,667 --> 01:44:52,083
Fala o tenente Harp.

1194
01:44:53,250 --> 01:44:54,250
Missão cumprida.

1195
01:44:56,042 --> 01:44:57,458
A regressar à base.

1196
01:44:58,792 --> 01:45:00,000
<i>Escuto.</i>

1197
01:45:00,083 --> 01:45:01,167
Recebido.

1198
01:45:02,000 --> 01:45:03,208
Bom trabalho, miúdo.

